---
title: Apricot Chicken Legs with Roasted Potato Wedges & Lemony Broccoli
description: Get a leg up at dinnertime with this recipe that has *all the flavors*, like apricot jam, Dijon mustard, and a hint of lemon swirled into a delectable glaze for crispy-skinned roasted chicken. Each bite of juicy dark meat feel like a revelation of sweet, savory, and tangy flavors. And it only gets better when you factor in the sides: potato wedges seasoned with warm spices and easy-peasy microwaved broccoli with a touch of lemon, butter, and chili flakes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5dfd137e39b70a23332c467e-62ac4b03.jpg
